channel.title: Emergency Team Needed Now! [District69]
channel.description:
Hello Moparscapers. This is Arsy's from EndlessPK & Sabsabi Online. [b]District 69 is in need of a Client Sided Coder.[/b] We will talk about our benefits once you are willing to help.. there's going to be a reward. You're obviously going to be part of our staff team which means you will be my co-owner. ~ District 69 includes: [b]Will Be Running on A VPS![/b] We really need a Client Side Coder!
All skills working. Many hidden things to do in the server ::pure, ::max (max hit), ::stats, ::yell (until we receive 75 players) Good economy, but you can still join and immediately pk You can actually play the server if you aren't a donator. Faster training ::requestmod which teleports a mod to you! All PvP Armour with Vesta longsword and statius spec 100% TELETABS Team capes with blue mini-map In-Game High Scores D Claws , Obtain @ Tormented Demonds Minigame! Zanik Crossbow Anchor , Obtaint @ Barellchest Minigame! DDS POISONS *HAWT* Lunar (Vengance) Kill/Death Ratio, Kill Streak, Pk Points/Kills, And More! CorpBeast + Spirit Shields Godwars with 100% working godswords 100% working duel arena Working Clan Chat A lot of custom party hats & more items! Slayer Point System! Refenrence Point System! Report System A fun, different version of Pest Control 100% Barrows A better version of Assault minigame 100% staffs with autocast New Jad minigame instead of boring-and-long 63 wave Fight Caves Chaotic Maul Much more realistic c'bows All potions + potion mixing Fun server events Awesome custom items no other servers have Staff of light Working DFS Granite maul specs immediately 100% WORKING TURMOIL + SOULSPLIT.
Please Reply then Contact me for more info.
PS: This server has been completely coded by me.
